{"word":"G1884 - ἐπαρκέω - eparkéō - ep-ar-keh'-o - Relieve","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπαρκέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eparkéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ar-keh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Relieve</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"உதவிசெய் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. to ward off or drive away"},{"paragraph":"2. to aid, give assistance, relieve"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G714 - ἀρκέω - arkéō - ar-keh'-o/714\">G714</a>; to <i>avail for</i>, that is, <i>help:</i> - relieve.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}